#24  It Takes a Queen's Village Air Date - Nov. 8 2013

Chris and Tad hope to come up big in the neighborhood of Queens Village; Mike B hopes to defeat Big Steve in a bidding war.


This only one of 4 episodes that aired on Nov. 8 that I could find.

Anyone else have any of these episodes they can share?


List of shows that aired Nov.8
------------------------------

26.
Drags to Riches

The buyers attend an auction in the Wallabout area of Brooklyn; Candy and Courtney keep an eye out for clothing; Big Steve tries to climb his way into a profit.


25.
Auction Haunters

Mike B thinks big and brings his cube truck to Amityville; Candy and Courtney look for vintage items; Joe P practices his golf swing.


24.
It Takes a Queen's Village

Chris and Tad hope to come up big in the neighborhood of Queens Village; Mike B hopes to defeat Big Steve in a bidding war.


23.
Bid Master Funk

The buyers visit a high-end facility in the Brooklyn neighborhood of Bushwick; Big Steve seeks items for man caves; Joe P uncovers funky stuff from the 1960s and '70s.
